目前MTK平台已添加HD默认图标显示，由于使用Asus SystemUI，需要Asus协助处理。
图片资源使用的是stat_sys_volte_icon.xml
首先在frameworks\base\packages\SystemUI\res\layout\signal_cluster_view.xml布局中添加显示：
<!-- M: Add for customized feature -->
<!-- M: Support "SystemUI HD Voice icon". @{ -->
<ImageView
	android:id="@+id/hd_voice_icon"
	android:layout_height="wrap_content"
	android:layout_width="wrap_content"
	android:visibility="gone"
	/>
<!-- M: Support "SystemUI HD Voice icon". }@ -->
<!-- Add for [VOLTE status icon] -->
在frameworks\base\packages\SystemUI\src\com\android\systemui\statusbar\SignalClusterView.java加载；

在frameworks\base\packages\SystemUI\src\com\android\systemui\statusbar\policy\MobileSignalController.java中监听更新图标：
   public void notifyListeners() {
	+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
        /// M: Support voLTE
        updateVolte();
	+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
        /// M: update plmn label @{
        mNetworkController.refreshPlmnCarrierLabel();
        /// @}
    }
	
    /// M: Support VoLte @{
    private void updateVolte() {
        if (mNetworkController.getImsRegState() == ServiceState.STATE_IN_SERVICE &&
            mSubscriptionInfo.getSubscriptionId() == mNetworkController.getImsSubId() &&
            !mNetworkController.isImsRegOverWfc()) {
            int slotId = mSubscriptionInfo.getSimSlotIndex();
            int iconId = isLteNetWork() ? mNetworkController.getVolteIconId(slotId) : 0;
            Log.d(mTag, "updateVolte: slotId: " + slotId + " iconId: " + iconId);
            mCallbackHandler.setVolteStatusIcon(iconId);
        }
    }

    public boolean isLteNetWork() {
        return (mDataNetType == TelephonyManager.NETWORK_TYPE_LTE
            || mDataNetType == TelephonyManager.NETWORK_TYPE_LTEA);
    }
	
在frameworks\base\packages\SystemUI\src\com\android\systemui\statusbar\policy\CallbackHandler.java中，实现：
    /// M: Add for [VOLTE status icon]
    @Override
    public void setVolteStatusIcon(final int iconId) {
        post(new Runnable() {
            @Override
            public void run() {
                for (SignalCallback signalCluster : mSignalCallbacks) {
                    signalCluster.setVolteStatusIcon(iconId);
                }
            }
        });
    }

最后在frameworks\base\packages\SystemUI\src\com\android\systemui\statusbar\SignalClusterView.java中设置图片资源，已经设置显示和隐藏即可：
    @Override
    public void setVolteStatusIcon(final int iconId) {
        if (iconId > 0) {
            /// M: customize VoLTE icon. @{
            mSignalClusterExt.customizeVoLTEIcon(mVolteIcon, iconId);
            /// M: customize VoLTE icon. @}
        }
        mVolteIcon.setVisibility(iconId > 0 ? View.VISIBLE : View.GONE);
    }

